  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nTo avoid having different behaviors with account creation and login between mobile and desktop apps, we should use these endpoints, instead of Login, SaveAccountAndLogin, LoginWithConfig, etc...\r\n\r\n- Login:\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-go/blob/238a6e2f2db453d748372721005c6ada7bce2435/mobile/status.go#L293\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-go/blob/develop/protocol/requests/login.go\r\n\r\n- Create Account\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-go/blob/238a6e2f2db453d748372721005c6ada7bce2435/mobile/status.go#L268C6-L268C27\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-go/blob/develop/protocol/requests/create_account.go\r\n\r\n- Restore Account and Login\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-go/blob/238a6e2f2db453d748372721005c6ada7bce2435/mobile/status.go#L268C6-L268C27\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-go/blob/develop/protocol/requests/restore_account.go \r\n\r\nCurrently there's no new endpoint for login with keycard so the existing one should still be used\r\n\r\ncc: @cammellos ",
